---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 121
By: Ananda Moyi
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=The Divine Allopathy
---
The soul that is without suffering does not feel the need of knowing the
ultimate cause of the universe. Sickness, grief, hardships, etc., are all
indispensable elements in the spiritual ascent.
